strings.Value: "That was a tough day. Want to relax? I have something nice in my flask!"
"Ughh! 'Nice' for those who want heartburn, an ulcer, and a three-week hangover! Put it away and don't take it back out. When we return to the capital, I'll treat you to something really good!"
"Knowing you, I would guess it's donkey piss, and as soon as we taste it, you'll laugh, saying, 'I said it was nice! And it's good for you too, ha ha ha hmmm!"
